<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Survey Results</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Survey Results</h1>
        <p>Total number of surveys: <%= total_surveys %></p>
        <p>Average Age: <%= avg_age.toFixed(2) %> years</p>
        <p>Oldest person who participated in survey: <%= oldest_age.toFixed(2) %> years</p>
        <p>Youngest person who participated in survey: <%= youngest_age.toFixed(2) %> years</p>
        <p>Percentage of people who like Pizza: <%= pizza_percentage.toFixed(2) %> %</p>